<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><legaldoc><law type="statute"><section><amendatorysection chaptername="Courts; Civil Procedure" statutenumber="25-306"><bookinfo>Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska</bookinfo><statuteno>25-306</statuteno><catchline>Wife's right to defend.</catchline><para>If a husband and wife be sued together, the wife may defend for her own right; and if the husband neglect to defend, she may defend for his right also.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>R.S.1867, Code &#167; 35, p. 398; </para><para>R.S.1913, &#167; 7587; </para><para>C.S.1922, &#167; 8530; </para><para>C.S.1929, &#167; 20-306; </para><para>R.S.1943, &#167; 25-306.</para></source></law></legaldoc>